# .gitignore — FcMobile
# Publish code + docs + example edl.json ONLY.
# Never commit copyrighted game footage, player cards, real-life photos, or BGM.

# ── Python ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]

# ── macOS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store

# ── Local-only tooling & personal notes (not part of the public project) ──
.claude/
PROGRESS.md
OCR_UPGRADE_PROMPT.md

# ── Heavy / copyrighted media — "bring your own" (see README) ──
*.mp4
*.MOV
*.mov
*.mp3
*.png
*.PNG
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.JPG
*.JPEG
*.webp
*.WEBP

# Ignore the CONTENTS of generated / material directories …
**/clips/**
**/highlights/**
**/output/**
**/assets/**

# … but keep the empty-folder skeleton so a fresh clone has the layout.
# (.gitkeep placeholders survive; the nested asset dirs are re-included so git can reach them.)
!**/assets/cards/
!**/assets/bgm/
!**/.gitkeep
